<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" modified="2024-07-01T20:20:20.675Z" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64; rv:127.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/127.0" etag="TwT7Vayz7QbQE3MPzCIQ" version="24.6.4" type="github" scale="1" border="0"> <diagram name="Page-1" id="-ifTIxoUpv2fot0Oa-qI"> <mxGraphModel dx="2890" dy="2800" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml
!define KUBERNETES #CCFFCC
!define CONTAINER #CCCCFF
!define DATABASE #FFCCCC
!define QUEUE #FFFFCC

skinparam componentStyle uml2

package \"Kubernetes Cluster\" as k8s KUBERNETES {
 component \"Capturador de Paquetes\" as packetCapture CONTAINER
 component \"Cola de Mensajes\" as messageQueue QUEUE
 component \"Analizador de Datos\" as dataAnalyzer CONTAINER
 component \"Motor de Reglas\" as ruleEngine CONTAINER
 component \"Generador de Alertas\" as alertGenerator CONTAINER
 database \"MongoDB\" as mongodb DATABASE
 component \"API Backend\" as apiBackend CONTAINER
 component \"Interfaz de Usuario\" as userInterface CONTAINER
 
 component \"Módulo de Machine Learning\" as mlModule CONTAINER
 component \"Módulo de Análisis de Comportamiento\" as behaviorModule CONTAINER
}

cloud \"Internet\" as internet
actor \"Usuario\" as user

internet -down-> packetCapture : Tráfico de Red

packetCapture -down-> messageQueue : Paquetes Capturados
messageQueue -down-> dataAnalyzer : Paquetes para Análisis

dataAnalyzer -down-> mongodb : Almacena Resultados
dataAnalyzer -right-> ruleEngine : Datos Analizados

mlModule -up-> dataAnalyzer : Asiste en el Análisis
behaviorModule -up-> dataAnalyzer : Asiste en el Análisis

ruleEngine -down-> alertGenerator : Actividades Sospechosas
alertGenerator -down-> mongodb : Almacena Alertas

apiBackend -up-> mongodb : Lee/Escribe Datos
userInterface -up-> apiBackend : Solicitudes HTTP

user -up-> userInterface : Interactúa

note right of packetCapture
 Captura tráfico de red
 en tiempo real
end note

note right of dataAnalyzer
 Procesa y analiza
 paquetes de red
end note

note right of ruleEngine
 Evalúa datos contra
 reglas predefinidas
end note

note right of alertGenerator
 Crea alertas basadas
 en actividades sospechosas
end note

note right of mlModule
 Aplica algoritmos de
 machine learning para
 detección de anomalías
end note

note right of behaviorModule
 Analiza patrones de
 comportamiento en el tráfico
end note

@enduml",
 "format": "svg"
}" id="a6KkYA9ZVtokGqkM21vC-1"> <mxCell style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1" parent="1"> <mxGeometry x="-829" y="14" width="1679" height="1072" as="geometry" /> </mxCell> </UserObject> </root> </mxGraphModel> </diagram> </mxfile>
